::{{DIcon|Talk}} Will there be more items later?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_304009710-->
:::'''Janus' Steed:''' Nope, that's it. Didn't I just say it was the end of the Passage? Unless the world resets itself, I've got nowhere else to scavenge more weird and wonderful things for you.
:::'''Janus' Steed:''' Besides, this is already the second batch. Still not enough for you? You must have a ton of memories to spare.
