::{{DIcon|Talk}} I want to have a chat with you.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_304009713-->
:::'''Janus' Steed:''' Hmph. Consider yourself lucky &mdash; talking to a divine foal is an honor. If I hadn't left my hometown, I'd charge you for this... Forget it. Just speak your mind.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Where do you get your stock from?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_304009715-->
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' The dawn of fate, the end of Passage, the rooftops of Talanton's estate, and Cerces' favorite restaurant...
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' Obviously, I made all that up. In other words &mdash; classified information. Don't ask. Just know they're all treasures.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Era Nova is coming, you...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_304009718-->
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' Era Nova? Oh, that prophecy! No wonder the monsters were acting up, I guess we're in for a ride. I even let an Okheman hide inside the divine foal for a bit.
::::'''Janus' Steed:''' Eh, works for me. This means I get to see the other divine foals again. And if I run into those slackers, I swear I'm painting their heads green.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I'll come back next time.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_304009721-->
:::'''Janus' Steed:''' Go ahead. Just don't forget to bring more memories!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
